// Test ta.roc (Rate of Change)
// ROC = ((current - N bars ago) / N bars ago) * 100, so it needs N+1 values.
// Over the last 6 bars close is 296..301.

// Bars: 6

// ((301 - 296) / 296) * 100
roc5 = ta.roc(close, 5)
log.info(roc5)

